            "title": "Assembly Biosciences GAAP EPS of -$0.55 beats by $3.01, revenue of $72.3M beats by $35.02M",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Assembly Biosciences <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20445516-assembly-biosciences-reports-year-end-2025-financial-results-and-recent-highlights\">press release</a>  (ASMB): FY  GAAP EPS of -$0.55 <font color=\"green\"> beats by $3.01</font>.</li>\n<li>Revenue of $72.3M (+153.5% Y/Y) <font color=\"green\"> beats by $35.02M</font>.</li>\n<li>Cash, cash equivalents and marketable securities were $248.1 million as of December 31, 2025, compared to $232.6 million as of September 30, 2025, and $112.1 million as of the year ended December 31, 2024. The company’s cash position is projected to fund operations into 2028.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
