            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Parsons Corporation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PSN\" title=\"Parsons Corporation\">PSN</a></span>) on Thursday said it had been awarded a classified U.S. government contract extension valued at more than $47 million.</li>\n<li>The award continues work the company has supported for over six years and includes two additional one-year option periods.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul><li>Source: <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20445523-parsons-awarded-47m-classified-contract-extension\">Press Release</a>\n</li></ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
